{"tid":1707654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(公投)聽朝先繼續定係繼續打埋今晚？","createTime":"2019-11-11T10:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:29:24.000Z","uid":28240,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2043ad5b3910199304d19e8d4b8d888b6bfb4c9","tid":1707654,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"基本上而家係人都知今朝其實係非常成功<br />\n基本上全港大部份嘅公司都會早放，就算啲人冇罷工返到公司都好早就返歸，相信返到公司都冇心情做嘢<br />\n<br />\n而且最重要係今次我地係有明確目標，就係強制罷工，而我哋今次呢一個行動已經初見成效，比較係星期六日冇任何目標嘅陣地戰好得多<br />\n<br />\n係咁而家問題㴝啦，冇人係可以打足廿四小時，但係我都好明白各位手足滿腔憤恨好想攞返公義，唔想就咁返屋企，相信好多香港人今日都有呢個感覺<br />\n而家大學俾狗圍，天已經黑晒，基本上一般嘅市民差唔多八點就會返晒屋企，條街剩低嘅只有街坊同手足，情況會變得有幾危險相信唔使我多講<br />\n我相信在場前線嘅手足，不過老實講我真係非常之擔心<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得應該要聽朝6點先繼續，定係今晚留守到最後一刻？我唔係話想散水，只係想大家討論下最有效嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽朝先繼續<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在場仲有手足，我要留守"},{"pid":"21e94952c94654c12aeb656f4ed292c347299bf8","tid":1707654,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e39fa1254663cca808ac797200e38d4d367ca418","tid":1707654,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3968a6c5fcad72d615e1bc98d7be78d78e05cf73","tid":1707654,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e649497006a4a0fbcfe15bffae5ef7523a2dacb","tid":1707654,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"引狗無差別襲擊準時返工打工仔，以後無人返工了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6e92ccd31f866363d319626bdd830c514dbd6a3","tid":1707654,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c788592b544f484101e488381be9b095c5f7184","tid":1707654,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81f8d8c3a2d2c0051c94d26bc19fb38c083931b1","tid":1707654,"uid":218309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bf7d7770d64c14fe5689a9c279df1990fbd0fde","tid":1707654,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:00:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">全民早起，繼續三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1EVZ9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1EVZ9E.jpg&h=f23d1a30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a771a38401b41979b40b10af76e9b9c2dca4f9c8","tid":1707654,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:00:15.000Z","msg":"聽朝繼續，今晚屋企張床要人"},{"pid":"bfad17abc9d72f548d8d772b66049420ff598a78","tid":1707654,"uid":303054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人講到幾多比幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}